foods.description: ULTRA THIN CRUST PIZZA, ULTIMATE COMBO
foods.lowercaseDescription: ultra thin crust pizza, ultimate combo
foods.ingredients: CHEESE: LOW MOISTURE PART SKIM MOZZARELLA CHEESE (CULTURED PASTEURIZED PART SKIM MILK, SALT, ENZYMES). SAUCE: WATER, TOMATO PASTE, MODIFIED FOOD STARCH, SUGAR, SALT, SPICES (INCLUDING OREGANO), MALTODEXTRIN, DEXTROSE, GARLIC AND ONION, CITRIC ACID, GUAR GUM, BEET POWDER, EXTRACTIVE OF PAPRIKA. SAUSAGE: PORK, WATER, SPICES, SALT, DEXTROSE, GARLIC POWDER, PAPRIKA. PEPPERONI: (PORK, BEEF, SALT, DEXTROSE, SODIUM NITRATE, BHA, BHT, CITRIC ACID, MAY CONTAIN WATER, SPICES, FLAVORING, SMOKE FLAVORING, PAPRIKA, OLEORESIN OF PAPRIKA, LACTIC ACID STARTER CULTURE, SODIUM ASCORBATE, GARLIC POWDER, DEHYDRATED GARLIC). PARMESAN: (MADE FROM PASTEURIZED PART-SKIM COW'S MILK, CULTURE, SALT, CORNSTARCH AND POWDERED CELLULOSE TO PREVENT CAKING). ASIAGO: (PASTEURIZED MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SALT, AND ENZYMES), POWDERED CELLULOSE (TO PREVENT CAKING). SPICE BLEND: SPICES (OREGANO, PEPPER, BASIL), MALTODEXTRIN, ONION & GARLIC, SOYBEAN OIL, PARSLEY. ULTRA THIN CRUST: ENRICHED FLOUR (WHEAT FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, ENZYME, FOLIC ACID), WATER, SOYBEAN OIL, YEAST, DEXTROSE, CALCIUM PROPIONATE (PRESERVATIVE), OLIVE OIL, SALT, DOUGH CONDITIONER (SODIUM METABISULFITE) AND SOY LECITHIN.
